overview: Young William Ospreay is literally flipping his way to the top of the wrestling world. Rob Naylor caught up with the cheeky young Brit after having a Meltzer rated 5 star match on night 2 of BOLA 2016.  Learn all about his early backyard days as Ace Pain, to blowing up twitter with Ricochet. Will also goes into hilarious detail about his encounter with the man they call Vader.  Don't miss this awesome interview with on of the brightest young talents in the business.
title: Hitting The Highspots - Will Ospreay
